		<layout-unit id="lay-1.04" xref="u-1.04 u-1.05 u-1.06">Helsinki promises an enchanting journey into a world of different architectural styles.</layout-unit>
		<layout-unit id="lay-1.05" xref="u-1.07 u-1.08 u-1.09">The monumental city centre is a unique neoclassical entity.</layout-unit>
		<layout-unit id="lay-1.06" xref="u-1.10 u-1.11 u-1.12">There are numerous buildings representing neo-styles in the centre of Helsinki, such as the beautifully conserved House of Estates (1890).</layout-unit>
